instructions:
## TASK: Select Best 3 Threat Models

The form only allows selecting up to 3 threat models (key concerns), but these 48 entities have more than 3.

For each entity, select the 3 MOST RELEVANT threat models based on:
1. The entity's category and type
2. Their regulatory stance and risk level
3. What the notes describe about their work/focus

Valid threat models: Labor displacement, Economic inequality, Power concentration, Democratic erosion, Cybersecurity, Misinformation, Environmental, Weapons, Loss of control, Copyright/IP, Existential risk, National security, Bias/discrimination

## OUTPUT FORMAT
{
  "selections": [
    { "entity_id": <id>, "keep": ["threat1", "threat2", "threat3"], "remove": ["threat4", ...], "reason": "<brief explanation>" }
  ]
}
